title: Dent de Nendaz
text: The Dent de Nendaz (literally "Tooth of Nendaz") is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> of the Swiss <a href="Pennine%20Alps">Pennine Alps</a>, overlooking <a href="Nendaz">Nendaz</a> in the canton of <a href="Valais">Valais</a>. Its summit can be easily reached from the cable car station of Tracouet (2,200 m).
